I believe the state capture tag is a euphemism directed at certain factions and  individuals instead of calling it  what it really is: the enrichment and protection of ANC congregants and associates. It occurred under  Nelson Mandela and  Thabo Mbeki, and  went into  overdrive  through the presidency of Jacob Zuma and his gluttonous ilk (the radical economic transformation brigade, whose red offshoot is the EFF). President Cyril Ramaphosa is therefore the current custodian, as  CEO of SA  Inc. Luyanda Marlon KamaKwaDwesi The FM welcomes concise letters from readers. They can be sent to fmmail@fm.co.za